dc_description_s: This data represents WIDNR classified trout locations in Wisconsin in 2015, and includes the layers 'WI_Classified_Trout_Polygon_2018', and 'WI_Classified_Trout_Lines_2018'.[Trout Waters are represented by Class I, Class II or Class III waters. These classes have specific ecological characteristics and management actions associated with them. For more information regarding Trout Classifications, see the Fisheries Trout Class Webpages. (https://dnr.wi.gov/topic/fishing/trout/streamclassification.html)]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.Individual REST Services are available for individual feature clases and are accessable from the following link: https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets?q=trout
